{"tid":1923261,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想戴豬嘴考DSE嘅學生/應屆請入（內附考評局回覆）","createTime":"2020-03-13T03:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T11:51:41.000Z","uid":308392,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a19eadf5eef9a007237e123574d09fe5ffd2e9","tid":1923261,"uid":308392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹其實好討厭戴口罩 四眼妹眼鏡會起霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以想戴豬嘴去考 但又驚唔比我考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是前幾日我就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打左電話</span>比考評局問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢大概就係答我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試場主任</span>會檢查 同埋可以email果件裝備過黎俾佢哋睇下合唔合規格喎<br />\n<br />\n我心諗個試場主任係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍絲</span></span>咪弊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我就心血來潮寫左封email問下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6O26q23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6O26q23.png&h=cb098cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果佢咁覆我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「考評局沒有限制口罩的種類」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">（即係可以戴？）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「惟我們須確保考試在公平公正的情況下進行。」</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">（即係豬嘴會影響公平性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGFcmBK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGFcmBK.png&h=d19daa63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都知自己有啲位問得唔清楚，所以而家再further問多啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以求安心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1TtEqV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1TtEqV.png&h=d422c71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲下考評局覆左會update 最緊要確保如果想戴豬嘴考試嘅巴絲都可以順利應試 祝各位DSE旗開得勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92e21ea2956145bee0a1eb574ac09088e1e6e10","tid":1923261,"uid":49471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"好波，私人送多副s80225比你入場"},{"pid":"0b859f5596abab92b893996f9d710d4bb1cb64ed","tid":1923261,"uid":196494,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬你封信錯晒格式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />考綜合前快d溫番公函點寫"},{"pid":"093a63d25018edc389b19e171683f20166c8aab5","tid":1923261,"uid":243834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"用email張圖佢就檢查到合唔合規定咁on9"},{"pid":"d0f24d64648adae35a82f21f1ea435e85396df4f","tid":1923261,"uid":308392,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0b859f5596abab92b893996f9d710d4bb1cb64ed","tid":1923261,"uid":196494,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬你封信錯晒格式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />考綜合前快d溫番公函點寫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47bZL8F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47bZL8F.gif&h=54f92cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左啲左右spacing有咩錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />綜合唔會寫敬啟者啦"},{"pid":"061c1232d3570c6e2eb745be3d81b1a9f94308f3","tid":1923261,"uid":308392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"093a63d25018edc389b19e171683f20166c8aab5","tid":1923261,"uid":243834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03: