5d12f78c95a824add98bff47145c9000","tid":1923261,"uid":191804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"其實你豬嘴上場都應該吹你唔脹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"其實唔會好焗咩 真心唔建議考試帶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"豬嘴舒服過戴外科口罩架，不過係就重咗少少同怕熱出汗唔舒服，但係考場嘅冷氣一般都開得幾勁所以應該無問題。"},{"pid":"7ac4fd601c3b769980f279e0f6fd764b80984c47","tid":1923261,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"【13/3 下午部分 Zoom lesson 😎】#由朝到晚撐住你💪🏻<br />\n溫馨提示：基本上全部課堂都設有錄影～同學唔洗擔心miss左，可以事後在我地Youtube channel重溫返課堂片段呀😉😉 有時部分課堂或者未必方便錄影，我地都會出返果一堂既雞精notes畀大家🥰特殊情況除外）<br />\n<br />\n4⃣ #中文 #卷一 #Paper1<br />\n日期：3月13日（五）晚上<br />\n時間：7:00pm- 9:30pm<br />\n🔔主題：①文本細讀技巧（錢鐘書《談教訓》非考核段落）<br />\n②從細讀到答題（錢鐘書《談教訓》考核段落，2019）<br />\n🟥YouTube 轉播🈶（只限聲音）<br />\n<br />\n5⃣ #ICT #資訊及通訊科技<br />\n日期：3月13日（五）晚上<br />\n時間：8:30pm- 10:30pm<br />\n🔔主題：2019 past paper + 電腦網絡+協定+互聯網應用<br />\n🟥YouTube 轉播🈶（只限聲音）<br />\n▶同學上堂之前可以做定 2019 past paper<br />\n<br />\n6⃣ #Econ #經濟 <br />\n日期：3月13日（五）晚上<br />\n時間：9:30pm- 11:00pm<br />\n🔔主題：money and banking 貨幣與銀行（清concept，做pastpaper）<br />\n🟥YouTube 轉播🈶<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n💮讀書時讀書，休息時休息。大家忙溫書嘅同時，記得都要俾自己放鬆下😉😉加油！💪🏻💪🏻😘💮<br />\n#2020DSE #DSE #DSE雞精聯盟<br />\n===========================<br />\n快啲follow晒我地嘅social media💻📱得到第一時間嘅資訊啦🌟<br />\n💙Facebook: DSE雞精聯盟2020<br />\n💜Instagram: @dsealliance2020<br />\n💚Telegram(channel): <a href=\"https://t.me/dsefighting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdsefighting&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=31603d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dsefighting</a><br />\n💛YouTube: DSE雞精聯盟2020<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBXNV9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBXNV9P.jpg&h=71eca052&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9e82bfd9fb3092149d9bf33dbc6aa9b0ee9c223","tid":1923261,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"&mdash;和你考&middot;香城考生限定&mdash;(派口罩+口罩套)<br />\n好多人見到考評局嘅口罩嚇到下巴都跌左落條頸到😱 今日收到好心人為考生捐出#外科口罩，並於以下派發，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n✏️學生需出示學生證/準考證比店員望一望<br />\n📖一包口罩有7個，每位學生獲發一包<br />\n🔍以每一張學生證/準考證計算<br />\n⛔️店員#不會抄低學生任何資料<br />\n<br />\n派發店鋪如下：<br />\n<br />\n📍<a href=\"http://Monala.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMonala.hk&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=2b06383d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Monala.hk</a>(⚠️開店時間）<br />\n旺角兆萬中心2樓204鋪<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/monalahk?igshid=qx0ynn6s5768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmonalahk%3Figshid%3Dqx0ynn6s5768&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=a30a2209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/monalahk?igshid=qx0ynn6s5768</a><br />\n<br />\n📍Maid Planet（⚠️23/3起能領取）<br />\n旺角豉油街24-26號福泰大廈11樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cafemaidplanet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcafemaidplanet%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=e1fb1f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cafemaidplanet/</a><br />\n<br />\n📍田園書屋<br />\n九龍旺角西洋菜街56 號2樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greenfieldbookstore/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreenfieldbookstore%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=0df423fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greenfieldbookstore/</a><br />\n<br />\n📍序言書室<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkreaders/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkreaders%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=690ceab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkreaders/</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: 有千幾個口罩想派手